          "_name": "header2",
          "_sourceTheme": "creatorm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"header2\" group=\"Headers\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"fullWidth\" title=\"Full Width\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <header>Slide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"List\" name=\"showList\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Button\" name=\"showButton\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Marker Color\" name=\"markerColor\" value=\"#fedb01\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Accent\" name=\"accentColor\" value=\"#eff0f6\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-between\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 b\">\n                <div class=\"gray\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/undraw-task-re-wi3v.svg\" alt=\"Mobirise\" class=\"align first\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/undraw-chore-list-re-2lq8.svg\" alt=\"Mobirise\" class=\"align second\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 t\">\n                <div class=\"right-side\">\n                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Vision &amp; Mission</b></h5>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .button-align, .list\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                        With more than 30 experts as the production crew as of December 2021, we have made ebullient productions for more than 10,00 clients, including media organizations, public-sector organizations, private companies and appreciably more individuals in Sokoto and across the northern states in Nigeria. The company’s experienced production crew have expertise in mass communication, languages, translations, media production, journalism and of course in Information and Communication Technology. This has enabled us to deliver the best media production and digital broadcasting services in Nigeria. We aim to keep up with Nigeria’s evolving digital economy industry. The vision of the Jikan Babi Production is to serve our clients producing the desired results, thereby rendering them high-quality services that surpass their expectations, and thus help in building an egalitarian society for our clients and the general public.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".list\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                        <li><b>Created for young entrepreneurs</b></li>\n                        <li><b>New videos every week</b></li>\n                        <li><b>Interviews with famous guests</b></li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <div class=\"button-align\">\n                        \n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "sUGNWAGSqU",
          "_anchor": "header2-a",
